Package: CloneTree
Title: Clonal Evolution QC and Visualization for Multi-Region Sequencing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("CloneTree", "Authors", email = "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Checks multi-region mutation cluster cancer cell fraction
    estimates against tumor evolution constraints and draws publication-style
    linear phylogenetic clone trees with annotated driver events.
